"use strict";
 
var count = 0;
 
module.exports = {
  uc_first: function uc_first(str) {
    return str.substring(0, 1).toUpperCase() + str.substring(1);
  },
  uuid: function uuid() {
    count += 1;
    return "uxcore-tinymce-" + count;
  },
  isEqual: function isEqual(a, b) {
    return JSON.stringify(a) === JSON.stringify(b);
  }
};
